description:
Quick how-to walking you through upgrading the firmware on your MK6 or G-Series Screen.  Don't freak out, its just 3 steps!

SquareWheels Sales & Support (AuCar MK6 and G-Series Screens):
https://www.squarewheelsauto.com

Join the G-Series Support Group! The coffee sucks but we're friendly!
https://www.facebook.com/groups/squarewheelsscreens

Here's a USB thumb drive:
https://amzn.to/3UwayGI

Chapters:
0:00  Intro
0:44 - Which screens does this work for?
1:18 - Where do the upgrades come from?
1:57 - Short version. 3 steps.
2:30 - Detailed Walkthrough
